name: Gym Membership
description: Burn more calories with a gym membership! More trips to the gym mean your metabolism is more active, you'll get fitter and burn more calories doing exercise.

name: NHS checkup
description: Regular trips to the doctor's means you can catch any health issues early. You'll live longer!

name: Fresh cooking
description: Fresh cooking means you don't eat junk food much, and instead dine on healthy options. You get more points per food!
